{"word":"G94 - ἄδικος - ádikos - ad'-ee-kos - Unjust","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄδικος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ádikos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ad'-ee-kos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unjust</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அநீதியுள்ள, அநீதியான, அநீதிமான்கள், அநீதர் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. unjust (of God as judge),"},{"paragraph":"2. of one who breaks God's laws, unrighteous, sinful"},{"paragraph":"3. of one who deals fraudulently with others"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G1349 - δίκη - díkē - dee'-kay/1349\">G1349</a>; <i>unjust</i>; by extension <i>wicked</i>; by implication <i>treacherous</i>; specifically <i>heathen:</i> - unjust, unrighteous.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G91/91\">G91</a>, <a href=\"#/G92/92\">G92</a>, <a href=\"#/G93/93\">G93</a>, <a href=\"#/G94/94\">G94</a>"}]}